            <h4>Real Strategy: Multiple Rooms + Events</h4>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>2 spare rooms</strong> at $85/night each = $170/night capacity</li>
              <li><strong>Event weekends</strong> (TIFF, Pride, etc.) command $150-200/room</li>
              <li><strong>Year-round operation</strong> with no arbitrary cutoff</li>
